{"tid":1640840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔好俾五毛混淆視聽]香港人拎中華民國國旗=揮動美國、英國國旗=純粹落中共面","createTime":"2019-10-09T06:44:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T04:33:39.000Z","uid":109923,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1583f24023f93671e9dcf91bff8873d144aff512","tid":1640840,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:44:43.000Z","msg":"香港人拎中華民國國旗落中共面，同台灣係冇必然關係<br />\n香港人拎中華民國國旗=揮動美國、英國國旗=<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">純粹對比10月1號落中共面</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n中共最驚就係中華民國國旗<br />\n你係香港揮台灣旗=港獨同台獨一齊玩=中共洗腦日常事項 WFC？<br />\n你係香港揮中華民國國旗=中共分分鐘唔夠薑報導，只敢blur咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/twapple/640pix/20160119/_Other/NEWS005.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n外國人舉中華民國旗，台灣綠營媒體會點樣睇？<br />\n<strong>就是挺台灣！南韓集會舉「中華民國國旗」 籲台韓恢復邦交</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LksWLDf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLksWLDf.png&h=b978385d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連深綠三立都未嫌棄，香港人請不要被五毛帶風向，過份解讀咗外國人舉中華民國國旗嘅意義</span><br />\n<br />\n台灣未脫離中華民國，未廢中華民國國旗<br />\n中華民國係台灣目前最大公約數，包括民進黨<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ox6zz0r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOx6zz0r.jpg&h=64d282cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ACfD1Fu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FACfD1Fu.jpg&h=e6b8f0c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何況10月10號本身就係中華民國國慶，而唔係台灣脫離中華民國獨立日<br />\n你雙十節拎支台灣旗出黎唔通係想踩台灣當前政權？<br />\n<br />\n我地&quot;今次&quot;唔係要為台灣主權帶風向，話要脫離埋中華民國明唔明呀！<br />\n台灣成功脫離中華民國獨立，咁你先至係獨立日當日舉台灣旗啦，點樣都唔關雙十事<br />\n<br />\n如果台灣主流已經去到脫離中華民國獨立，咁前一步會係嘗試先修改中華民國憲法變成兩個中國。依家中華民國憲法都仲未改，兩個中國方案都未曾嘗試，點會一下子跳咗step飛到直接放棄中華民國變成台灣國？<br />\n<br />\n台灣正名公投連台南都只係五五開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />區區一班香港人仲想幫台灣正名？<br />\n同意票多於不同意票的行政區包括：臺南市（52.73%）、嘉義縣（51.59%）、屏東縣（50.46%）、宜蘭縣（50.41%）"},{"pid":"091afaef0ba3f4aa680d972acec806eb47c52886","tid":1640840,"uid":109923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:49:46.000Z","msg":"[突發] iOS 13將會地區性禁台灣同香港國旗emoji<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1640698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1640698</a><br />\n<br />\n舉中華民國國旗亦可以同APPLE事件互相呼應，爭取更多嘅國際關注，尤其要俾美國人意識到美國企業奶共危機，希望長遠可以影響美國選舉同政策"},{"pid":"1903dfbec7a4c12ebe0b5461ef97892fba5b8cc0","tid":1640840,"uid":313764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:50:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLCPmok.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLCPmok.jpg&h=d80cc8eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日話要爭取國際線支持，我依家開左個英文版連儂牆啦，全部同我入去瘋狂貼文宣!<br />\n<br />\n[English] LIHKG Lennon Wall ver 1.0<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1640768\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1640768</a>"},{"pid":"388a0236211f16b79b0f30cb60e37172122e9224","tid":1640840,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:04:20.000Z","msg":"補自由時報<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2808979\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2808979&d=h%2FIbyvsQTNyUi2WbZ%2BJFJ%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=14aa78e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2808979&h=cd64c3a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2808979</a><br />\n<br />\n中華民國國旗=台灣國旗<br />\n<img src=\"http://67.205.139.234/images/210727_1570608024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F67.205.139.234%2Fimages%2F210727_1570608024.png&h=7ef70844&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d23cf4329f360f71fe53a6bef2dbb40b9d1c196","tid":1640840,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:08:59.000Z","msg":"舉中華民國國旗可以同APPLE EMOJI事件互相呼應，又激中共，又可以對APPLE表態<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f950fe8182f78b91b21c55cb9a81c5b9876fa8ff","tid":1640840,"uid":198278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LSKFtPT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLSKFtPT.gif&h=c0f05109&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd6ee7da974411d27edae532529aefc4be0b5513","tid":1640840,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T09:01:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">國際戰線要人!！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">呢排國際上發生左幾單重要打<br />\nNBA、south park 、暴雪、red bull <br />\n大家點可以呢個時候懶！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>係時候要世界明白中國有幾醜惡!</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">國際戰線！全球抗共！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n任務：<br />\n1. Twitter 戰線 請用Tg入面既Twitter help<br />\n2 YouTube 英文短片<br />\n3. Reddit戰線</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我地只有令全世界明白香港係幫自由世紀抵擋邪惡國家既先鋒，先可以令世人支持我地！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea6fa86b17fdfac69f91aa9d4f25b1402abcc5af","tid":1640840,"uid":226594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:02:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />共產黨好驚"},{"pid":"6d72307134412954295169f3c02d035f108f399e","tid":1640840,"uid":226594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee28ded295a7de62ed558ce35a60d99e0db8f5d","tid":1640840,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:06:42.000Z","msg":"巴哈姆特成班毒撚夠唔夠綠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求其搵個post，只見嫌棄韓國瑜褻瀆&amp;消費國旗（見正評）<br />\n冇人嫌棄國旗因為佢代表韓國瑜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「將中華民國國旗=韓國瑜」係國民黨文宣策略嚟，你哋唔係信真呀？<br />\n信嘅人先至係韓粉囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7DOSkid.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7DOSkid.png&h=b5c15c12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Axnr9by.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAxnr9by.png&h=2623dbe7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b69aRpT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb69aRpT.png&h=66f8e841&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EJ2LFie.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEJ2LFie.png&h=b5c41fa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rLLdPbz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrLLdPbz.png&h=27605e87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UA1gMYe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUA1gMYe.png&h=304d7d2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MqVpVRA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMqVpVRA.png&h=99ff6efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bg7DfRA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBg7DfRA.png&h=983e39ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0